
  Welcome to the SharkOS live installer 🦈

  The installer starts automatically and lays down a base Arch system.
  After you reboot, the full SharkOS desktop installs itself on first
  boot — no further steps needed.

  If you need a plain shell instead, switch to another console with
  Ctrl-Alt-F2, or re-run the installer any time with:

      sharkos-install

  Networking: wired is automatic; for Wi-Fi use `iwctl`.

